flowchart TD
    A[Metacognition] --> B[Metacognitive Knowledge]
    A --> C[Metacognitive Regulation / Control]
    A --> D[Metacognitive Experiences & Judgments]
    B --> B1[Declarative: what/that]
    B --> B2[Procedural: how]
    B --> B3[Conditional: when/why]
    C --> C1[Planning]
    C --> C2[Monitoring]
    C --> C3[Debugging / Error correction]
    C --> C4[Evaluation]
    C --> C5[Strategy selection & resource allocation]
    D --> D1[Prospective judgments: EOL, JOL, FOK]
    D --> D2[Retrospective judgments: confidence]
    D --> D3[Metacognitive feelings: difficulty, familiarity, TOT]
    E[Object-level cognition: perception, memory, reasoning, action] -->|monitoring signals| F[Meta-level model]
    F -->|control signals| E
    G[Social / collaborative context] --> A
    G --> H[Metacognitive dialogue and socially shared regulation]
    I[Domain dimension] --> J[Domain-specific components]
    I --> K[Domain-general components]
    J --> A
    K --> A
